title: syscall: documentation for `compileCallback` is wrong
body: The comment at https://github.com/golang/go/blob/master/src/syscall/syscall_windows.go#L110 refers to `asm_windows.a`, which doesn't exist. It should point to https://github.com/golang/go/blob/master/src/runtime/syscall_windows.go#L43 instead.
